sections.text:
The intersection is the room that connects both corridors. It always features a safer zone equipped with beds as well as an entrance to a chamber. In addition to that:
- intersection_1 and intersection_2 feature an ominous vault ;
- intersection_2 and intersection_3 feature an intersection barrel ;
- intersection_2 features a secret room with an additional bed and a decorated pot always containing 3 strings .
